00:30:56.229 --> 00:30:57.522
Ce, camera mea?

00:31:02.944 --> 00:31:03.945
Bun așa.

00:31:04.029 --> 00:31:04.863
Da.

00:31:08.617 --> 00:31:11.411
Dac-ar fi să semeni cu cineva,
pe cine-ai alege?

00:31:11.953 --> 00:31:13.955
